For the 1990 marketing year in the sheepmeat sector:
1.  the basic price is hereby fixed at ECU 432,32 per 100 kilograms carcase weight;
2.  the intervention price is hereby fixed at ECU 367,47 per 100 kilograms carcase weight;
3.  the derived intervention price applicable in region 4 is hereby fixed at ECU 347,66 per 100 kilograms carcase weight.
